# Keep the Docker build context minimal so only files required to install are copied by `COPY . .`.
**

# Build/install metadata required by pyproject.toml
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!README.md
!LICENSE

# Runtime package files
!fakesnow/

# Python cache artifacts in subdirs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# macOS in subdirs
**/.DS_Store
